Synopsis:
Yash Raj Filmsâ€™ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love storyâ€¦and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple questionâ€¦do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Filmsâ€™ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love storyâ€¦and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple questionâ€¦do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Video Song | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:

Lyrics:
Orupodhum visuvasathai vittuvidaadheergal
(Never let go of the faith)
Neengal visuvasithaal ellam koodumae 
(If you believe, everything will be possible)

Kadugalavu visuvasam irundhale podhum
(If you have mustard-seed sized faith,)
Yengugindra kaariyangal ellamae aagum
(Whatever you long for will happen)

Siricha mugamai varuvaaru
(With a smiling face, He will come)
Sirandhadhai ellamai tharuvaaru
(He will give you the best of everything)

1. Yobuvin vaazhkaiyai pola 
(Like the life of Job,)
Pala vidha (pala pala) kashtangal soola 
(In the midst of many kinds of trouble,)
Soraamal kartharai nee pidithukondal
(If you hold on to the Lord without growing weary,)

Yobuvin aasirvadham unaku undu 
(Jobâ€™s blessing belongs to you)
Ilanthadhai irandu madangaai petrukondu
(You will get back whatever you have lost in double measure)
Ini sezhipaaga nee vazhndhidu
(From now on, you will live prosperously)

2. Kulandhaiyin selvathirkaaga 
(For the gift of child,)
Yaengidum saaraalaaga 
(Longing like Sarah,)
Pala naatkal kaathirundhu azhugindraaiyo
(Have you been tearfully waiting many days?)

Abraghamin aasirvadham unaku undu 
(Abrahamâ€™s blessing belongs to you)
Naalaanaalum nichaiyamaaga mudivu undu 
(Even though it takes time, surely there is an end)
Un nambikkai veen pogaadhu
(Your hope will not be cut off)

â„— 2025 Stella Ramola

snippet.title: Sheesha (HD Video) Sabba | Meavin | In Flow (EP) New Punjabi Songs 2025 | Latest Punjabi Songs 2025
snippet.description:
One Take Worldwide Presents

Song - Sheesha
Singer - SABBA
EP - In Flow 
Lyrics & Composer - Sabba
Music - Meavin
Producer - Meeru
Artwork - Garry Nawab
Label - One Take Worldwide

Lyrics :

Mai surma ne paaya,
Tu tareef kari akkhan di.
Shaapan challe laa teh,
Tu tareef kari hathan di.
Laune haar teh shingar bhi mai chaddteh ve,
Gena gatta chakkya ne mai.
Ve tu jiddhan da keha mainu soni,
Audhon da sheesha takkya ne mai âœ¨ (x2)
Haye jeenu jeenu keha tu balona b mai chaddya,
Oh ni suit paya jeda tenu naiyo fabbya.
Haye tere piche kinna kuj chad ke bethi aan,
Haye tu he mainu kite chadd javin na ve sabbeya.
Tenu bahr ne pasand jana mera,
Karon per pattya ne mai.
Ve tu jiddhan da keha mainu soni,
Audhon da sheesha takkya ne mai  (x2)
Hayee samne bethake mainu vendha rahe gaur naal,
Teh kahen is mukh nu makeup di b lorh na.
Vadh jeh gram audhon khoon mutiyar da ve,
Jadon kahe tere yahi dunia teh haur na.
Lagg nazar jave na saddi yaari nu,
Sehliyan nu dassya ne mai.
Ve tu jiddhan da keha mainu soni,
Audhon da sheesha takkya ne mai  (x2)
